OL,3,CInspection of maternity service finds
OL,4,C'babies could be put at risk of harm'
OL,6,FAn inspection has found "poor
OL,7,Fgovernance and ineffective systems" at
OL,8,Fa maternity unit in Banbury, could put
OL,9,Fwomen and babies "at risk of harm".
OL,11,FMaternity services at Horton General
OL,12,FHospital have been rated as requires
OL,13,Fimprovement, following an inspection
OL,14,Fby the Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,15,Fin October.
