OL,6,FThe hospital said it was improving.
OL,8,FMilica Redfearn, Director of Midwifery
OL,9,Fat Oxford University Hospitals, said:
OL,10,F"We are disappointed by this result
OL,11,Fbut we always welcome feedback on ways
OL,12,Fto improve our services and we will
OL,13,Fwork with staff, women, and birthing
OL,14,Fpeople to make the improvements
OL,15,Fsuggested. We have a great team at the
OL,16,FHorton Midwifery-led Unit as the
OL,17,Finspectors found when they visited."
