OL,3,CInspection of maternity service finds
OL,4,C'babies could be put at risk of harm'
OL,6,FCarolyn Jenkinson, said "We found
OL,7,Fexamples of poor record-keeping, and
OL,8,Fpeople using the service weren't
OL,9,Falways being risk assessed. The
OL,10,Fmidwife-led unit used a national tool
OL,11,Fto assess whether someone giving birth
OL,12,Fwas at risk of deteriorating, but
OL,13,Fstaff weren't always completing these
OL,14,Frecords and leaders didn't audit them."
