OL,4,C'babies could be put at risk of harm'
OL,6,F"It was also concerning that safety
OL,7,Fequipment wasn't always checked
OL,8,Fregularly, which meant some out-of-
OL,9,Fdate equipment and products might be
OL,10,Fused on people."J"Staff weren't always
OL,11,Frecognising and reporting incidents
OL,12,Fand near misses when they should have
OL,13,Fbeen."J"We'll be monitoring the trust
OL,14,Fclosely, including through future
OL,15,Finspections, to make sure women,
OL,16,Fpeople using the services and their
OL,17,Fbabies are safe."
