OL,6,FFollowing the inspection, the ratings
OL,7,Ffor Horton General Hospital have also
OL,8,Fchanged. The overall rating for the
OL,9,Fhospital has been downgraded from good
OL,10,Fto requires improvement, as have the
OL,11,Fareas of safe and well-led.JThe
OL,12,Foverall rating for Oxford University
OL,13,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust remains
OL,14,Fas requires improvement.JProfessor
OL,15,FMeghana Pandit, Chief Executive
OL,16,FOfficer at Oxford University
OL,17,FHospitals, said: "As a learning
OL,18,Forganisation we will improve services
OL,19,Falong the lines highlighted in the
OL,20,Freport, although I am disappointed for
OL,21,Fthe staff who have been working so
OL,22,Fhard to make improvements already.J"I
OL,23,Fwant to be very clear that our
OL,24,Fcommitment to the Horton General
OL,25,FHospital is unwavering, and although
